","value":"This working group will champion the strategy and oversee broad operational\naspects of JupyterCon, including event operations and community leadership for\nthe event.","position":{"start":{"line":37,"column":1},"end":{"line":37,"column":1}},"key":"EzoK5IKWaJ"}],"key":"SlHfxyYXSX"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":41,"column":1},"end":{"line":41,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Operations and Budget","position":{"start":{"line":41,"column":1},"end":{"line":41,"column":1}},"key":"X1pYxyv4A1"}],"identifier":"operations-and-budget","label":"Operations and Budget","html_id":"operations-and-budget","implicit":true,"key":"Xgqv3fQbUG"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":43,"column":1},"end":{"line":44,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"This working group will collaborate with the Jupyter Executive Council to serve\nas stewards for Project Jupyter funds for events in this committee’s purview.","position":{"start":{"line":43,"column":1},"end":{"line":43,"column":1}},"key":"LwUKitr4K2"}],"key":"M3sgKdleuo"},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"position":{"start":{"line":46,"column":1},"end":{"line":46,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Diversity, Equity, Inclusion","position":{"start":{"line":46,"column":1},"end":{"line":46,"column":1}},"key":"Dxz8Xj8iGj"}],"identifier":"diversity-equity-inclusion","label":"Diversity, Equity, Inclusion","html_id":"diversity-equity-inclusion","implicit":true,"key":"prj53fRW8W"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":48,"column":1},"end":{"line":53,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Project Jupyter is an engaged and respectful community made up of people from\nall over the world. This working group pledges to foster a productive,\nharassment-free environment for everyone who participates in organizing or\nattending our events. We recognize our work is a highly visible and\npotentially impactful way for diversity, equity, and inclusion (DEI)